TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT max(CS_POSITIONRELATION.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE) as EFFECTIVESTARTDATE, max(CS_POSITIONRELATION.EFFECTIVEENDDATE) as EFFECTIVEENDDATE, PRN.NAME as PARENTPOSITIONNAME, CHLD.NAME as CHILDPOSITIONNAME, TYP.NAME as POSITIONRELATIONTYPE FROM CS_POSITIONRELATION INNER JOIN cs_positionrelationtype TYP ON CS_POSITIONRELATION.removedate = to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND CS_POSITIONRELATION.islast=1 AND TYP.removedate = to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND TYP.DATATYPESEQ=CS_POSITIONRELATION.positionrelationtypeseq INNER JOIN cs_position PRN ON PRN.REMOVEDATE = to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND prn.islast =1 AND PRN.ruleelementownerseq = CS_POSITIONRELATION.parentpositionseq INNER JOIN cs_position CHLD ON CHLD.REMOVEDATE = to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND CHLD.islast =1 AND CHLD.ruleelementownerseq = CS_POSITIONRELATION.childpositionseq group by PRN.NAME , CHLD.NAME, TYP.NAME

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: PARENTPOSITIONNAME = IN_PARENTPOSITIONNAME AND CHILDPOSITIONNAME = IN_CHILDPOSITIONNAME AND POSITIONRELATIONTYPE = IN_POSITIONRELATIONTYPE
